10:57:03 AM [express] GET /api/admin/marketing/queue 304 in 3ms :: [{"id":"434df4c4-b09b-4c57-99be-c4b881fe58cc","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"card_news","caption":"Guess what Gukdung's absolute fave treat is? 🦘\n\nKangaroo! Yep, this discerning 8-year-old Jindo has impeccable taste. While he's not usually fussed about food (unlike SOME dogs we know 👀), there's something about premium Aussie roo that gets his tail wagging.\n\nHypoallergenic, lean, and packed with protein – it's the perfect choice for our sophisticated Seoul boy. Even picky eaters can't resist! 🇦🇺✨\n\nWhat's your pup's ultimate weakness?","hashtags":"#KangarooTreats #JindoLove #PremiumPetFood #SpoiltDogsAU #HealthyDogTreats #AussieRoo #PickyEaterApproved #KoreanJindo #DogTreatsAustralia #LuxuryPetLife","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/card_1775126880990_bvyfy3kym5.jpg","videoUrl":null,"imagePrompt":"Square format Instagram carousel image. Scene 1: A dignified 8-year-old cream-colored Korean Jindo dog (Gukdung) sitting elegantly with a single kangaroo treat in front of him, looking interested and refined. Soft natural lighting, premium aesthetic. Text overlay at top: 'Gukdung's #1 Treat' in modern sans-serif font. Text at bottom: 'Kangaroo 🦘' in elegant script. Clean white or soft beige background with subtle Australian native botanical elements. Professional pet photography style, sharp focus on dog's expressive face, warm color palette.\n\n=== STYLE GUIDELINES ===\n[하네스 착용]\n야외 이미지인경우 하네스를 항상 착용.\n실내이미지인경우 아무것도 착용하지않음\n\n[자연스러운이미지 생성]\n너무 AI 스럽지않은 이미지 생성.\n너무 심한 아웃포커스 금지.\n너무 정확한 구도, 완벽한 표정 하지말기. - 국둥이가 카메라를 정면으로 바라보고있는 장면 피하기. \n너무 께끗하고 예쁘기만한 배경 하지말기.\n실생활에서 어설프게 찍은 이미지느낌 재현\n\n[배경설정]\nFree form post 인경우항상 같은 배경 유지:\n- 실내: 짙은 남색 카페트 바닥, 크림색 린넨 소파, 자연광\n- 실외: 시드니 Bicentennial Park, 초록 잔디, 자연스러운 환경","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"국둥이가 제일 좋아하는 간식은 캥거루","createdAt":"2026-04-02T10:35:09.774Z"},{"id":"7e8c9b70-c790-46e3-a2cb-d04a92d54fe0","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"card_news","caption":"Sometimes doing absolutely nothing is the ultimate luxury. 🤍\n\nAt 8 years old, Gukdung has mastered the art of simply being. No tricks to perform, no toys to chase, no treats to beg for. Just pure, elegant existence.\n\nAnd honestly? That's rather magnificent.\n\nBecause the best dogs don't need to do anything to be everything. 🐾","hashtags":"#SpoiltDogs #KoreanJindo #JindoLife #LuxuryPetLife #PetBoutiqueAustralia #SimplePleasures #DogWisdom #SeniorDogLove #ElegantCanine #DoingNothing #PerfectAsIs #AustralianPets #PremiumPetCare","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/card_1775125506902_q7vpjmatq7.jpg","videoUrl":null,"imagePrompt":"A serene Korean Jindo dog with white and tan fur lying gracefully on a luxurious cream linen cushion near a sunlit window, peaceful expression, soft natural lighting, minimalist aesthetic, premium interior setting with muted tones, gentle shadows, the dog appears content and calm doing nothing, elegant composition, text overlay space at top reading 'Doing Nothing is an Art Form', square format, 1:1 aspect ratio, sophisticated and calming atmosphere\n\n=== STYLE GUIDELINES ===\n[하네스 착용]\n야외 이미지인경우 하네스를 항상 착용.\n실내이미지인경우 아무것도 착용하지않음\n\n[자연스러운이미지 생성]\n너무 AI 스럽지않은 이미지 생성.\n너무 심한 아웃포커스 금지.\n너무 정확한 구도, 완벽한 표정 하지말기. - 국둥이가 카메라를 정면으로 바라보고있는 장면 피하기. \n너무 께끗하고 예쁘기만한 배경 하지말기.\n실생활에서 어설프게 찍은 이미지느낌 재현\n\n[배경설정]\nFree form post 인경우항상 같은 배경 유지:\n- 실내: 짙은 남색 카페트 바닥, 크림색 린넨 소파, 자연광\n- 실외: 시드니 Bicentennial Park, 초록 잔디, 자연스러운 환경","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"아무것도 못하는 국둥이 이대로도 좋아.","createdAt":"2026-04-02T10:22:14.747Z"},{"id":"6a6125a6-ff47-4690-acc9-bdede9700b1d","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"card_news","caption":"Some dogs fetch. Some do tricks. Gukdung? Gukdung simply *exists* — and honestly, that's more than enough. 🐾✨\n\nAt 8 years old, this distinguished Korean Jindo has perfected the art of doing absolutely nothing... and looking fabulous while at it. No food obsession. No toy drama. Just pure, unbothered elegance.\n\nBecause sometimes the best thing your dog can do is just be themselves. And we wouldn't change a single whisker. 💛","hashtags":"#SpoiltDogs #KoreanJindo #JindoLove #SeniorDogLove #LuxuryPets #AustralianPetBoutique #DogsOfInstagram #JustBeingGukdung #PerfectAsYouAre #PremiumPetLife","imageUrl":null,"videoUrl":null,"imagePrompt":"Square format lifestyle photograph of an elegant 8-year-old cream-colored Korean Jindo dog named Gukdung lying peacefully on a luxurious cream linen sofa, looking serene and content with soft natural lighting from a window. Minimalist Scandinavian-inspired interior with muted tones. Text overlay space at top reading 'DOES NOTHING. PERFECT AT IT.' in elegant serif font. Premium pet lifestyle aesthetic, soft focus background, warm colour palette, sophisticated composition.\n\n=== STYLE GUIDELINES ===\n[하네스 착용]\n야외 이미지인경우 하네스를 항상 착용.\n실내이미지인경우 아무것도 착용하지않음\n\n[자연스러운이미지 생성]\n너무 AI 스럽지않은 이미지 생성.\n너무 심한 아웃포커스 금지.\n너무 정확한 구도, 완벽한 표정 하지말기. - 국둥이가 카메라를 정면으로 바라보고있는 장면 피하기. \n너무 께끗하고 예쁘기만한 배경 하지말기.\n실생활에서 어설프게 찍은 이미지느낌 재현\n\n[배경설정]\nFree form post 인경우항상 같은 배경 유지:\n- 실내: 짙은 남색 카페트 바닥, 크림색 린넨 소파, 자연광\n- 실외: 시드니 Bicentennial Park, 초록 잔디, 자연스러운 환경","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"아무것도 못하는 국둥이 이대로도 좋아.","createdAt":"2026-04-02T10:19:56.949Z"},{"id":"9b4e9eec-2abd-4c90-a12b-81a5640ad384","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"reel","caption":"Beach bum Gukdung reporting for duty 🏖️\n\nWhile other dogs are doing zoomies, our distinguished 8-year-old Jindo is conducting a very serious inspection of the shoreline. Selective about food? Yes. Picky about toys? Absolutely. But give him a beach walk and suddenly he's writing poetry with his paws in the sand.\n\nSpoilt? Perhaps. Beach-obsessed? Undeniably. 🌊\n\nWhat's your pup's happy place?","hashtags":"#SpoiltDogs #JindoLove #BeachDog #AustralianPets #LuxuryPetLife #CoastalDog #DogWalks #PremiumPetBoutique #JindoLife #BeachVibes","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/img_1775125116987_vg9mv2bgxj.jpg","videoUrl":"https://v3b.fal.media/files/b/0a94a03f/uBfaVN0rOcpjPDiSgBCaE_output.mp4","imagePrompt":"Real-time speed, normal motion, not slow motion. An 8-year-old Korean Jindo wearing a harness walks steadily along the sandy shoreline at Sydney beach. The dog moves at a calm, measured pace, occasionally pausing to sniff the sand or glance toward the water. Waves gently lap at the shore in the background. The camera follows with natural handheld movement, capturing the dog's relaxed gait from a slight side angle as it strolls through shallow water and wet sand. Natural daylight, realistic outdoor beach environment. Normal playback speed. No cinematic slow motion.","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"바다에 놀러간 Gukdung","createdAt":"2026-04-02T10:16:30.310Z"},{"id":"e0439378-8208-4173-8fdc-cdc3dba5033c","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"card_news","caption":"When you take an 8-year-old Jindo to the countryside and suddenly he's a puppy again 🌾✨\n\nGukdung might not be the most playful pup these days, but something about wide open fields just hits different. No food obsession needed when you've got endless grass to sniff and gentle breezes to contemplate.\n\nThat distinguished senior energy + countryside vibes = pure magic 🐕💛\n\nSwipe to see our boy living his best meadow life →","hashtags":"#JindoLife #SeniorDogLove #CountrysidePup #GukdungAdventures #AustralianPets #PremiumPetLife #SpoiltDogsAU #KoreanJindo #DogWellness #NatureWalks","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/img_1775124670457_6291i5zup27.jpg","videoUrl":null,"imagePrompt":"Square format photo-realistic image of a cream-colored Korean Jindo dog, 8 years old, standing gracefully in a golden grass meadow during golden hour. The dog has a calm, dignified expression with slightly pointed ears and alert eyes. Soft sunlight filtering through, creating a warm glow. Wildflowers scattered in the field. Text overlay space at top: 'Field Day with Gukdung' in elegant serif font. Bottom space for: 'Sometimes the simplest walks are the best walks'. Aspect ratio: 1:1 square. Photographic style with slight film grain, warm color grading, peaceful countryside atmosphere. Dog positioned slightly off-center, looking into the distance with that classic Jindo composure.\n\n=== STYLE GUIDELINES ===\n[하네스 착용]\n야외 이미지인경우 하네스를 항상 착용.\n실내이미지인경우 아무것도 착용하지않음\n\n[자연스러운이미지 생성]\n너무 AI 스럽지않은 이미지 생성.\n너무 심한 아웃포커스 금지.\n너무 정확한 구도, 완벽한 표정 하지말기. - 국둥이가 카메라를 정면으로 바라보고있는 장면 피하기. \n너무 께끗하고 예쁘기만한 배경 하지말기.\n실생활에서 어설프게 찍은 이미지느낌 재현\n\n[배경설정]\nFree form post 인경우항상 같은 배경 유지:\n- 실내: 짙은 남색 카페트 바닥, 크림색 린넨 소파, 자연광\n- 실외: 시드니 Bicentennial Park, 초록 잔디, 자연스러운 환경","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"들에 놀러간 gukdung","createdAt":"2026-04-02T10:08:43.864Z"},{"id":"0f24aec6-abdb-4bcd-8ff8-eda3b886dd24","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"reel","caption":"When Gukdung spots a rabbit, eight years of dignity evaporate instantly. 🐰💨\n\nOur sophisticated Jindo transforms into a furry missile with exactly one brain cell dedicated to THE CHASE. No food obsession? Not interested in toys? Darling, that's because he's been saving ALL his energy for this exact moment.\n\nThe rabbit always wins. But does Gukdung learn? Absolutely not. That's what we call commitment to the craft. 🎯\n\nDoes your pup have their own 'forget everything I know' trigger?","hashtags":"#SpoiltDogs #JindoDog #KoreanJindo #AussieDogsofInstagram #DogReels #RabbitChase #DogHumour #PremiumPetLife #SydneyDogs #MelbourneDogs #LuxuryPets #DogLife #Gukdung #DogsofAustralia #PetBoutique","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/img_1775124438623_g816tcfoy4.jpg","videoUrl":"https://v3b.fal.media/files/b/0a949ffb/vH2lK7o54gq0sSugbw09S_output.mp4","imagePrompt":"Real-time speed, normal motion, not slow motion. Korean Jindo dog suddenly lunges forward on leash at Bicentennial Park, pulling hard toward distant rabbit in grass. Dog's body tenses, feet scrambling on ground, head locked forward in intense focus. Handler struggles to maintain grip as dog strains against harness. Handheld camera follows the jerky, chaotic movement - slight shake as camera operator moves with the action. Natural realistic movement of excited dog mid-chase attempt, feet kicking up dirt, tail rigid. Normal playback speed. No cinematic slow motion.","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"토끼쫓는 국둥이","createdAt":"2026-04-02T09:59:46.374Z"},{"id":"766e8c6b-d47f-479c-a31b-206adddd9904","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"reel","caption":"When the ball is life but you're too dignified to admit it 🎾✨\n\nGukdung pretends he's not obsessed with fetch... until that tennis ball appears. Then suddenly this 8-year-old Jindo becomes a Olympic athlete.\n\nThe quiet ones always surprise you 😏\n\nWhat's your pup's secret obsession?","hashtags":"#SpoiltDogs #JindoLove #BallObsessed #LuxuryPetLife #AustralianDogs #DogReels #FetchLife #KoreanJindo #8YearsYoung #PremiumPets #SydneyDogs #PetBoutique","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/img_1775123648750_t20irdb58uj.jpg","videoUrl":"https://v3b.fal.media/files/b/0a949fac/b56S5vIkz4cM0vYri567U_output.mp4","imagePrompt":"Eight-year-old Korean Jindo stands on green grass at Bicentennial Park Sydney, appearing calm and disinterested. A tennis ball enters frame from left side. Dog's head turns sharply toward ball, ears perk up. Dog lunges forward, accelerating from standing position into full sprint. Body extends in running motion, legs pumping naturally. Camera follows handheld style, slight shake, capturing dog mid-chase. Ball bounces once on grass. Dog closes distance rapidly, mouth opens to catch. Natural daytime speed, realistic movement, no slow motion. Outdoor lighting, green grass background visible throughout motion.","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"공놀이가 세상에서 제일좋아.","createdAt":"2026-04-02T09:52:06.127Z"},{"id":"4f81c157-bd3d-429b-a575-b6de69b5b6e5","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"reel","caption":"Golden hour strolls with my favourite philosopher 🌅\n\nGukdung doesn't do fetch. Doesn't do tricks. Just does... profound contemplation at sunset. Honestly, we could all learn something.\n\nWhat's your dog's favourite time for walkies?","hashtags":"#SpoiltDogs #GoldenHourWalks #JindoLife #ParkLife #SunsetStrolls #AustralianPets #LuxuryPetLife #DogWalks #PetPhotography #JindoDog","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/img_1775122071881_favgve0mpto.jpg","videoUrl":"https://v3b.fal.media/files/b/0a949f0f/oSd_ZlkP8VcQJBQo-DMlx_output.mp4","imagePrompt":"A majestic white Korean Jindo dog named Gukdung walking gracefully through a lush Australian park at golden hour, warm sunset light filtering through eucalyptus trees, long shadows on grass, peaceful contemplative mood, premium lifestyle photography aesthetic, cinematic composition, vertical format, 9:16 ratio\n\n=== STYLE GUIDELINES ===\n[하네스 착용]\n야외 이미지인경우 하네스를 항상 착용.\n실내이미지인경우 아무것도 착용하지않음\n\n[자연스러운이미지 생성]\n너무 AI 스럽지않은 이미지 생성.\n너무 심한 아웃포커스 금지.\n너무 정확한 구도, 완벽한 표정 하지말기. - 국둥이가 카메라를 정면으로 바라보고있는 장면 피하기. \n너무 께끗하고 예쁘기만한 배경 하지말기.\n실생활에서 어설프게 찍은 이미지느낌 재현\n\n[배경설정]\nFree form post 인경우항상 같은 배경 유지:\n- 실내: 짙은 남색 카페트 바닥, 크림색 린넨 소파, 자연광\n- 실외: 시드니 Bicentennial Park, 초록 잔디, 자연스러운 환경","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"해질무렵 공원산책중","createdAt":"2026-04-02T09:24:26.063Z"},{"id":"730550f7-bacc-40ec-9238-e080364422cf","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"feed_image","caption":"아침 산책? 아니, 아침 행차라고 해야겠어요 👑\n\n8살 진돗개가 호숫가 전체를 소유한 것처럼 걷는 모습이라니 (스포: 실제로 그의 것이에요). 저 품격 있는 뒤뚱거림, 저 초연한 에너지, '나 다 겪어봤어, 인간아' 하는 분위기.\n\nGukdung에게 아침 산책이란 없습니다. 아침 행차만 있을 뿐이죠. 🐕‍🦺✨\n\n이 정도 여유가 있다면, 나이는 그저 숫자일 뿐이에요.","hashtags":"#SpoiltDogsAU #진돗개라이프 #아침산책 #프리미엄반려생활 #호주공원 #호주반려견산책 #진돗개 #진돗개사랑 #반려견일상 #럭셔리펫 #호주펫부티크 #반려견스타일 #시니어독사랑 #공원산책","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/img_1775112610738_bgz8kusexq.jpg","videoUrl":null,"imagePrompt":"Rear view photograph of a white Korean Jindo dog walking away from camera on a park path, wearing a premium harness with leash visible, confident proud gait, morning golden hour lighting, serene lake visible in background, manicured park grounds with trees, the dog's tail held high showing excitement and dignity, professional pet photography style, natural colors, square format, 1:1 ratio\n\n=== STYLE GUIDELINES ===\n[하네스 착용]\n야외 이미지인경우 하네스를 항상 착용.\n실내이미지인경우 아무것도 착용하지않음\n\n[자연스러운이미지 생성]\n너무 AI 스럽지않은 이미지 생성.\n너무 심한 아웃포커스 금지.\n너무 정확한 구도, 완벽한 표정 하지말기. - 국둥이가 카메라를 정면으로 바라보고있는 장면 피하기. \n너무 께끗하고 예쁘기만한 배경 하지말기.\n실생활에서 어설프게 찍은 이미지느낌 재현\n\n[배경설정]\nFree form post 인경우항상 같은 배경 유지:\n- 실내: 짙은 남색 카페트 바닥, 크림색 린넨 소파, 자연광\n- 실외: 시드니 Bicentennial Park, 초록 잔디, 자연스러운 환경","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"아침산책. 위풍당당한 발걸음","createdAt":"2026-04-02T06:49:27.706Z"},{"id":"e00c4869-2b41-45e3-8266-43c8131c6e90","promptId":null,"productId":null,"platform":"instagram","contentType":"feed_image","caption":"미스터리 공 사냥꾼이 또 출동했습니다 🔮⚽️\n\n매번. 정말. 매번이에요. 공원에 가면 Gukdung은 덤불 속으로 사라졌다가 누군가가 오래전에 잃어버린 테니스공을 물고 나타나요. 훈련도 안 했고, 간식으로 유도한 것도 아니에요. 순수한 보물 사냥 본능이죠.\n\n오늘의 발견품은? 아마도 2019년부터 실종된 것으로 추정되는 흙투성이 윌슨 공. 지금은 마치 미제 사건을 해결한 것처럼 당당하게 앉아있네요 🕵️‍♂️\n\n진짜 궁금한 게, 공 가져오기에는 전혀 관심 없는 8살 진돗개가 어떻게 공원의 비공식 분실물 센터가 된 거죠? 완전히 '놀고 싶은 게 아니라 증거를 수집하고 싶어' 바이브인데요 😂\n\n혹시 여러분 강아지도 이상한 초능력 가진 친구 있나요? 아래에 댓글 남겨주세요 👇","hashtags":"#SpoiltDogs #KoreanJindo #진돗개라이프 #공원나들이 #보물사냥꾼 #GukdungChronicles #시니어독 #호주멍스타그램 #프리미엄펫부티크 #강아지성격 #특별한강아지 #공수집가 #도그스타그램 #진돗개 #국둥이","imageUrl":"https://ssqzvozouagsslczmaxj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/generated-images/img_1775111862841_ooj9xk7n5wn.jpg","videoUrl":null,"imagePrompt":"A dignified Korean Jindo dog with cream-colored fur sitting upright in front of overgrown bushes and wild grass at a dog park, a muddy tennis ball placed directly in front of his paws, the dog has an alert but calm expression with pointed ears, mature 8-year-old appearance, natural lighting, shallow depth of field with bushes slightly blurred in background, the dog looks proud but nonchalant like a detective who just cracked a case, Australian park setting with eucalyptus trees visible in distant background, square format, 1:1 ratio, photorealistic style\n\n=== STYLE GUIDELINES ===\n[자연스러운이미지 생성]\n너무 AI 스럽지않은 이미지 생성.\n너무 심한 아웃포커스 금지.\n너무 정확한 구도, 완벽한 표정 하지말기.\n너무 께끗하고 예쁘기만한 배경 하지말기.\n실생활에서 어설프게 찍은 이미지느낌 재현\n\n[배경설정]\nFree form post 인경우항상 같은 배경 유지:\n- 실내: 짙은 남색 카페트 바닥, 크림색 린넨 소파, 자연광\n- 실외: 시드니 Bicentennial Park, 초록 잔디, 자연스러운 환경","status":"approved","approvedBy":"admin","scheduledAt":null,"postedAt":null,"makeWebhookId":null,"metaPostId":null,"rejectionReason":null,"topic":"dog park 에만 가면 어디선가 공을 물어오는 국둥이","createdAt":"2026-04-02T06:37:15.208Z"}]
